history.content: We will, of course, try to accommodate declared cs majors who have a final lower division cs class still to take (61C or 70).  You may need to reach out to me after your phase 2 appointment as well as be flexible about discussion section schedule.

Hi, I have a question about enrollment categories for cs70.

Currently, I'm a sophomore intending to declare CS this semester with early declaration. 

I have not yet taken cs70 and plan to do so next semester. However, I noticed that the enrollment categories have reserved seats for undeclared L&S, and eecs. Because I won't be undeclared anymore by phase 2, will I still be able to get into the class? Or should I phase 1 cs70?
history.subject: Enrollment Priorities/Categories for CS70
